description: Add support for Amazon CloudWatch Logs
Add support for Amazon Cognito Service

Update ``aws route53`` command to the latest version
Update ``aws ec2`` command to the latest version

Fix bug where using the ``aws s3 mv`` command to move a large file onto itself results in the file being deleted (`issue 831 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/issues/831>`__)

Fix issue where ``python.exe`` is on a path that contains spaces (`issue 825 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/pull/825>`__)
